Once you use the VH Network Assist tool, you need to connect to your VH-109 to configure it for your team.
Connect an ethernet cable from your computer to the VH-109 and navigate to 192.168.69.1 in your web browser.

Detailed insructions can be found here:
https://frc-radio.vivid-hosting.net/overview/programming-your-radio-at-home
